\v 3 Some people came, bringing to him a paralysed man, who was being carried by four of them. 
\v 4 They were unable to get him near to Jesus, because of the crowd, so they removed the roof above Jesus, and, when they had made an opening, they let down the mat on which the paralysed man was lying. 
