\v 26  \wj \+w So\+w*, \+w if\+w* \+w Satan\+w* \+w is\+w* \+w in\+w* revolt \+w against\+w* \+w himself\+w* \+w and\+w* \+w is\+w* \+w divided\+w*, \+w he\+w* \+w cannot\+w* last – \+w his\+w* \+w end\+w* \+w has\+w* \+w come\+w*!\wj* 
\p
\v 27  \wj ‘\+w No\+w* \+w man\+w* \+w who\+w* \+w has\+w* broken \+w into\+w* \+w a\+w* \+w strong\+w* \+w man\+w*’s \+w house\+w* \+w can\+w* carry off \+w his\+w* \+w goods\+w*, \+w without\+w* \+w first\+w* tying \+w him\+w* \+w up\+w*; \+w and\+w* \+w not\+w* \+w until\+w* \+w then\+w* \+w will\+w* \+w he\+w* \+w plunder\+w* \+w his\+w* \+w house\+w*.\wj* 
