\v 18  \wj \+w Those\+w* \+w meant\+w* \+w by\+w* \+w the\+w* seed \+w sown\+w* \+w among\+w* \+w the\+w* brambles \+w are\+w* different; \+w they\+w* \+w are\+w* \+w the\+w* \+w people\+w* \+w who\+w* hear \+w the\+w* \+w message\+w*,\wj* 
