\b
\p
\v 32 Presently they came to a garden known as Gethsemane, and Jesus said to his disciples \wj ‘\+w Sit\+w* \+w down\+w* \+w here\+w* \+w while\+w* \+w I\+w* \+w pray\+w*.’\wj* 
